end foreach document #set($discard = $spacesToBeChanged.add($spaceTBChanged)) #end ## end if results is not empty (the space was found on this wiki) #end ## end foreach space #end ## end foreach wiki #end ## end if($wikisToBeChanged.size()!=0) #end ##end macro {{/velocity}} {{velocity}} ## ##First page ## #set($logger = $services.logging.getLogger("PAUL_Display_Log")) #set($discard = $logger.warn("START OF SCRIPT")) #if("$!{request.getQueryString()}" == '') #set($redirectLink = "$!{doc.getURL()}") {{html wiki=true}} This application lets you run simple scripts on all the documents specified by the fields below.
**If any of the fiels are left empty, it will be applied to all wikis/spaces/document in their specific area of search**.
**Complete using comma separated values. (ex: Blog, Sandbox, Admin)**
{{warning}} Be careful when targeting specific documents. This script will modify all documents sharing the specified name from all the specified wikis. A list of all the documents that your script will be applied to, will be displayed in the next step. {{/warning}}

spaces
